   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>... (Having entered) the bath with a number of other persons he went off with my outer garment. I therefore ask you, if you see fit, to order a letter to be sent to the proper official to summon him before you, in order that he may be punished for this at the tribunal and by this punishment you may deter others from like courses. If this is done, I shall have found energetic succour at your hands. Farewell.</ab>
